properties.name: Path
properties.expression: const scaleFacs = thisLayer.content('Admin').content('Scaling Factors').transform.scale[0];const C1 = thisLayer.content('Limb').content('Lower Group').content('Shoe').content('ball circle').position;const C2 = [0,0];const R1 = thisLayer.content('Limb').content('Lower Group').content('Shoe').content('ball circle').size[0] * 0.5;const R2 = thisLayer.content('Limb').content('Lower Group').content('Shoe').content('ankle circle').size[0] * 0.5;let heelBack = thisLayer.effect('High Top')('Heel Back Offset') * scaleFacs;// Handle weird glitch when heel back offset is equal to ankle radiusconst P = [R2 + thisLayer.effect('High Top')('Heel Depth Offset') * scaleFacs, ((heelBack == R2) ? heelBack + 0.001 : heelBack)];function norm(v){ return Math.sqrt(v[0]*v[0]+v[1]*v[1]); }function cross(a,b){ return a[0]*b[1]-a[1]*b[0]; }function almostEqual(a,b){ return Math.abs(a-b) < 1e-6; }function samePoint(a,b){    return almostEqual(a[0], b[0]) && almostEqual(a[1], b[1]);}function pointTangents(P,C,r){    const v = sub(P,C);    const d = norm(v);    const base = Math.atan2(v[1], v[0]);    const phi = Math.acos(r/d);    const ang1 = base + phi;    const ang2 = base - phi;    const t1 = add(C, [Math.cos(ang1)*r, Math.sin(ang1)*r]);    const t2 = add(C, [Math.cos(ang2)*r, Math.sin(ang2)*r]);    return [t1,t2];}function outerTangents(A,ra,B,rb){    const v = sub(B,A);    const d = norm(v);    const base = Math.atan2(v[1],v[0]);    const theta = Math.acos((ra - rb)/d);    const ang1 = base + theta;    const ang2 = base - theta;    const A1 = add(A,[Math.cos(ang1)*ra, Math.sin(ang1)*ra]);    const B1 = add(B,[Math.cos(ang1)*rb, Math.sin(ang1)*rb]);    const A2 = add(A,[Math.cos(ang2)*ra, Math.sin(ang2)*ra]);    const B2 = add(B,[Math.cos(ang2)*rb, Math.sin(ang2)*rb]);    return [A1,B1,A2,B2];}function convexHull(pts){    pts.sort(function(a,b){ return a[1]==b[1]?a[0]-b[0]:b[1]-a[1]; });    const p0 = pts[0];    pts.sort(function(a,b){        return Math.atan2(a[1]-p0[1], a[0]-p0[0]) - Math.atan2(b[1]-p0[1], b[0]-p0[0]);    });    const h=[pts[0],pts[1]];    for(let i=2;i<pts.length;i++){        while(h.length>1){            const p1=h[h.length-2], p2=h[h.length-1];            if(cross(sub(p2,p1),sub(pts[i],p2))>0) break;            h.pop();        }        h.push(pts[i]);    }    return h;}let pts = [];pts.push(P);pts = pts.concat(pointTangents(P,C1,R1));pts = pts.concat(pointTangents(P,C2,R2));pts = pts.concat(outerTangents(C1,R1,C2,R2));let hull = convexHull(pts);// If resulting hull does not contain the single point P (point is interior),// rotate the hull so the first vertex is the hull vertex closest to Plet startIndex = -1;for (let i=0;i<hull.length;i++){    if (samePoint(hull[i], P)){ startIndex = i; break; }}if (startIndex === -1){    // find nearest hull vertex to P    let best = 0;    let bestd = Infinity;    for (let i=0;i<hull.length;i++){        const d = norm(sub(hull[i], P));        if (d < bestd){ bestd = d; best = i; }    }    startIndex = best;}// rotate hull to start from startIndexfunction rotateArray(arr, k){    const n = arr.length;    const out = [];    for (let i=0;i<n;i++) out.push(arr[(k + i) % n]);    return out;}if (hull.length > 0) hull = rotateArray(hull, startIndex);createPath(hull, [], [], 1);

properties.expression: // lozengefunction midPoint(p1, p2, per) {    return [p1[0] + (p2[0] - p1[0]) * per, p1[1] + (p2[1] - p1[1]) * per];}function tangentsAbsolute(vertices, tans) {    for (let i = 0, il = vertices.length; i < il; i++) {        tans[i] = add(tans[i], vertices[i]);    }    return tans;}function tangentsRelative(vertices, tans) {    for (let i = 0, il = vertices.length; i < il; i++) {        tans[i] = sub(tans[i], vertices[i]);    }    return tans;}function flipX(point) {    return [-point[0], point[1]];}function flipArrayY (vertices, flipPoint) {    for (let i = 0; i < vertices.length; i++) {        vertices[i] = [vertices[i][0], flipPoint - (vertices[i][1] - flipPoint)]    }    return (vertices)}const endctrl = thisComp.layer('{{ end }}');const scaleFacs = thisLayer.content('Admin').content('Scaling Factors').transform.scale[0];const dist = endctrl.effect('Pseudo/skl_3bone_data_01')('ikfkfreeksides').value[0]; const circ2 = thisLayer.effect('High Top')('Pant Middle Width') * scaleFacs * 0.5;const circ1 = thisLayer.effect('High Top')('Pant Start Width') * scaleFacs *0.5;let c1, c2;if (circ2 < circ1) {	c2 = circ2, c1 = circ1	} else {	c1 = circ2, c2 = circ1	}const A = Math.acos(clamp((c1 - c2) / dist, -1, 1));const fac = 0.5522847498307933;const topSemiVerts = [[c2, -dist], [0, -dist - c2], [-c2, -dist]];const topSemiIns = [[0, 0], [(c2 * fac), 0], [0, -c2 * fac]];const topSemiOuts = [[0, -c2 * fac], [-c2 * fac, 0], [0, 0]];const quad = (0.5 * Math.PI);const t = linear(quad - A, 0, quad, 0, 1);const topSemiInsAbs = tangentsAbsolute(topSemiVerts, topSemiIns);const topSemiOutsAbs = tangentsAbsolute(topSemiVerts, topSemiOuts);let Q0 = midPoint(topSemiVerts[0], topSemiOutsAbs[0], t);let Q1 = midPoint(topSemiOutsAbs[0], topSemiInsAbs[1], t);let Q2 = midPoint(topSemiInsAbs[1], topSemiVerts[1], t);let R0 = midPoint(Q0, Q1, t);let R1 = midPoint(Q1, Q2, t);let S0 = midPoint(R0, R1, t);let newTopSemiVerts = [S0, topSemiVerts[1], [-S0[0], S0[1]]];let newTopSemiIns = tangentsRelative(newTopSemiVerts, [R0, Q2, flipX(R1)]);let newTopSemiOuts = tangentsRelative(newTopSemiVerts, [R1, flipX(Q2), flipX(R0)]);const botSemiVerts = [[c1, 0], [0, -c1], [-c1, 0]];const botSemiIns = [[0, 0], [(c1 * fac), 0], [0, -c1 * fac]];const botSemiOuts = [[0, -c1 * fac], [-c1 * fac, 0], [0, 0]];const remSemiVerts = [[-c1, 0], [0, c1], [c1, 0]];const remSemiIns = tangentsAbsolute(remSemiVerts, [[0, 0], [-(c1 * fac), 0], [0, c1 * fac]]);const remSemiOuts = tangentsAbsolute(remSemiVerts, [[0, c1 * fac], [c1 * fac, 0], [0, 0]]);const botSemiInsAbs = tangentsAbsolute(botSemiVerts, botSemiIns);const botSemiOutsAbs = tangentsAbsolute(botSemiVerts, botSemiOuts);Q0 = midPoint(botSemiVerts[0], botSemiOutsAbs[0], t);Q1 = midPoint(botSemiOutsAbs[0], botSemiInsAbs[1], t);Q2 = midPoint(botSemiInsAbs[1], botSemiVerts[1], t);R0 = midPoint(Q0, Q1, t);R1 = midPoint(Q1, Q2, t);S0 = midPoint(R0, R1, t);const newBotSemiVerts = [flipX(S0), remSemiVerts[0], remSemiVerts[1], remSemiVerts[2], S0]const newBotSemiIns = tangentsRelative(newBotSemiVerts, [flipX(R1), flipX(Q0), remSemiIns[1], remSemiIns[2], R0])const newBotSemiOuts = tangentsRelative(newBotSemiVerts, [flipX(R0), remSemiOuts[0], remSemiOuts[1], Q0, R1])newTopSemiVerts.push(newBotSemiVerts[0], newBotSemiVerts[1], newBotSemiVerts[2], newBotSemiVerts[3], newBotSemiVerts[4]);newTopSemiIns.push(newBotSemiIns[0], newBotSemiIns[1], newBotSemiIns[2], newBotSemiIns[3], newBotSemiIns[4]);newTopSemiOuts.push(newBotSemiOuts[0], newBotSemiOuts[1], newBotSemiOuts[2], newBotSemiOuts[3], newBotSemiOuts[4]);let state;if (circ2 < circ1) {	state = 1;	} else {	state = 2;    newTopSemiVerts = flipArrayY(newTopSemiVerts, -dist * 0.5)    newTopSemiIns = flipArrayY(newTopSemiIns, 0)    newTopSemiOuts = flipArrayY(newTopSemiOuts, 0)}createPath(newTopSemiVerts, newTopSemiIns, newTopSemiOuts, true)
